--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Third-party material vendored or used at runtime
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

This repository vendors a copy of the Connect protobuf surface from the
Grafana Alloy "alloy-remote-config" project, used by the Fleet Manager
to speak the same `collector.v1.CollectorService` RPC that Grafana Cloud
Fleet Management exposes:

    proto/collector/v1/*.proto
    Source : https://github.com/grafana/alloy-remote-config
    License: Apache-2.0

The runtime container image baked from `apps/fleet-manager/Dockerfile`
copies the `alloy` binary out of the upstream `grafana/alloy` image and
invokes it for `alloy fmt` syntax validation:

    https://github.com/grafana/alloy
    License: Apache-2.0

The Terraform provider (`terraform/provider-fleet`) is built against the
HashiCorp Terraform Plugin Framework:

    https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform-plugin-framework
    License: MPL-2.0 (used in unmodified form, dynamic dependency only)

All other third-party dependencies are declared in the per-language
manifests (`package.json`, `go.mod`) and retain their respective
upstream licenses.
